[package]
name = "async-compression"
version = "0.4.5"
authors = [ "Wim Looman <wim@nemo157.com>", "Allen Bui <fairingrey@gmail.com>",]
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
keywords = [ "compression", "gzip", "zstd", "brotli", "async",]
categories = [ "compression", "asynchronous",]
repository = "https://github.com/Nullus157/async-compression"
description = "Adaptors between compression crates and Rust's modern asynchronous IO types.\n"

[features]
all = [ "all-implementations", "all-algorithms",]
all-implementations = [ "futures-io", "tokio",]
all-algorithms = [ "brotli", "bzip2", "deflate", "gzip", "lzma", "xz", "zlib", "zstd", "deflate64",]
deflate = [ "flate2",]
gzip = [ "flate2",]
lzma = [ "xz2",]
xz = [ "xz2",]
zlib = [ "flate2",]
zstd = [ "libzstd", "zstd-safe",]
zstdmt = [ "zstd", "zstd-safe/zstdmt",]
deflate64 = [ "dep:deflate64",]

[dependencies]
memchr = "2"
pin-project-lite = "0.2"

[dev-dependencies]
bytes = "1"
futures = "0.3.5"
futures-test = "0.3.5"
ntest = "0.9"
proptest = "1"
proptest-derive = "0.4"
rand = "0.8.5"

[dependencies.brotli]
version = "3.3"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]

[dependencies.bzip2]
version = "0.4.4"
optional = true

[dependencies.flate2]
version = "1.0.13"
optional = true

[dependencies.futures-core]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false

[dependencies.futures-io]
version = "0.3"
default-features = false
features = [ "std",]
optional = true

[dependencies.libzstd]
package = "zstd"
version = "0.13"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.24.2"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.xz2]
version = "0.1.6"
optional = true

[dependencies.zstd-safe]
version = "7"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.deflate64]
version = "0.1.5"
optional = true

[dev-dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.24.2"
default-features = false
features = [ "io-util", "macros", "rt-multi-thread", "io-std",]

[dev-dependencies.tokio-util]
version = "0.7"
default-features = false
features = [ "io",]

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[package]
name = "flate2"
authors = [ "Alex Crichton <alex@alexcrichton.com>", "Josh Triplett <josh@joshtriplett.org>",]
version = "1.0.28"
edition = "2018"
license = "MIT OR Apache-2.0"
readme = "README.md"
keywords = [ "gzip", "deflate", "zlib", "zlib-ng", "encoding",]
categories = [ "compression", "api-bindings",]
repository = "https://github.com/rust-lang/flate2-rs"
homepage = "https://github.com/rust-lang/flate2-rs"
documentation = "https://docs.rs/flate2"
description = "DEFLATE compression and decompression exposed as Read/BufRead/Write streams.\nSupports miniz_oxide and multiple zlib implementations. Supports zlib, gzip,\nand raw deflate streams.\n"

[dependencies]
crc32fast = "1.2.0"

[dev-dependencies]
rand = "0.8"

[features]
default = [ "zlib",]
any_zlib = [ "any_impl",]
any_impl = []
zlib = [ "any_zlib", "libz-sys",]
zlib-default = [ "any_zlib", "libz-sys/default",]
zlib-ng-compat = [ "zlib", "libz-sys/zlib-ng",]
zlib-ng = [ "any_zlib", "libz-ng-sys",]
cloudflare_zlib = [ "any_zlib", "cloudflare-zlib-sys",]
rust_backend = [ "miniz_oxide", "any_impl",]
miniz-sys = [ "rust_backend",]

[dependencies.libz-sys]
version = "1.1.8"
optional = true
default-features = false

[dependencies.libz-ng-sys]
version = "1.1.8"
optional = true

[dependencies.cloudflare-zlib-sys]
version = "0.3.0"
optional = true

[dependencies.miniz_oxide]
version = "0.7.1"
optional = true
default-features = false
features = [ "with-alloc",]

[dev-dependencies.quickcheck]
version = "1.0"
default-features = false

[package.metadata.docs.rs]
all-features = true
rustdoc-args = [ "--cfg", "docsrs",]

[target."cfg(all(target_arch = \"wasm32\", not(target_os = \"emscripten\")))".dependencies.miniz_oxide]
version = "0.7.1"
default-features = false
features = [ "with-alloc",]

[source.vendored-sources]
directory = "cargo/vendor"

[source.crates-io]
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/armchairdevelopers/async-compression"]
git = "https://github.com/armchairdevelopers/async-compression"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"

[source."https://github.com/armchairdevelopers/flate2-rs"]
git = "https://github.com/armchairdevelopers/flate2-rs"
replace-with = "vendored-sources"
